('BEHAVIORAL', 'Medium', 'Tell me about a time when you had to deal with a difficult team member. How did you handle the conflict?', 'I ignored them and did the work myself.', 'I reported them to the manager immediately.', 'I set up a 1-on-1 meeting to listen to their perspective and find common ground.', 'I argued with them during the team meeting.', 'C', 'Using the STAR method, addressing conflict directly, privately, and constructively shows leadership and teamwork.', 'Conflict Resolution, Teamwork'),
('BEHAVIORAL', 'Hard', 'Describe a situation where you had to meet a tight deadline but realized you were behind schedule. What steps did you take?', 'I worked 24 hours straight without communicating to the team.', 'I missed the deadline and apologized later.', 'I prioritized tasks, asked for help, and communicated the revised timeline to stakeholders.', 'I compromised on the code quality completely.', 'C', 'Effective prioritization, seeking help, and proactive communication are key traits of a reliable engineer.', 'Time Management, Communication'),
